            "title": "Intro 2",
            "id": 126856,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Une façon de répéter des lignes de code est de les écrire encore et encore, mais cela prend vraiment beaucoup de temps si nous voulons créer des programmes plus grands.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"82\" endIndex=\"83\" /><option startIndex=\"83\" endIndex=\"92\" /><option startIndex=\"92\" endIndex=\"93\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>\"</code> suivi de <code>and again</code> et enfin <code>\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Intro 3",
            "id": 126857,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Pour construire des programmes et des applications plus grands, nous répétons des lignes de code en utilisant une <strong>boucle while</strong>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"if\" /></content></option><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"5\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>while</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "While keyword",
            "id": 126858,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Utiliser une boucle while pour répéter des lignes de code commence par le mot-clé <code>while</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;and again&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"5\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"and again\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"...\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de rentrer <code>while</code>.</p></body></html>"
